Actor Will Smith is in early talks to play the Genie in Disney&#8217;s live-action &#8216;Aladdin&#8217; movie.As Genie, the 48-year-old star would follow in the footsteps of Robin Williams, whose performance in the original 1992 animated film helped propel it to box office success and critical acclaim.&#8216;Sherlock Holmes&#8217; director Guy Ritchie is helming the new Aladdin movie, working from a script by John August.The project comes amid a wave of beloved Disney toons being remade as live-action movies.This article first appeared on Times of India 